                    # A few of the plugins (e.g. motion blur, mat filt) define
                    # meaningful tags in addition to the phase-based tags above.
                    #
                    # 2. The "priority" and "displayName" fields are required
                    # fields for "hydra plugins"; the former isn't relevant for
                    # scene index plugins, and the latter isn't used yet.
                    # 
